#ÌòëÏ∞¨ LOOKING FOR A PLAN IN SEOUL? @doota_official IS YOUR PLACE! üõçü©∑

Shopping at Doota Mall in Dongdaemun is always
an amazing experience! The mall offers a great selection
of popular brands like Nike, Timberland, Converse, LifeWork,
MLB, and even Olive Young a must visit if you love K-beauty and skincare. The layout is modern and easy to navigate, making it enjoyable to explore each floor.

One of the newest additions is Rundot, which just
opened recently. It's a paradise for sports lovers,
offering a wide range of athletic gear, apparel,
and accessories that blend style and performance perfectly.

Another highlight is the B2 floor, filled with restaurants
serving both Korean and international cuisine.
It's the perfect place to recharge and enjoy a
tasty meal during your shopping day.

Whether you're looking for fashion, sportswear,
or beauty products, Doota Mall has something for everyone.
I spent the entire day there and didn't even realize how fast time flew by

If you're in Seoul, I definitely recommend adding Doota Mall to your itinerary it's a great place to shop, eat, and enjoy a full day out!
